<plot>DANCING ALONE focuses on a young man named Mark and his struggles to deal with the loss of his one true love. With the terrible accident that sent her away three years ago, behind him, one day he sees her father. Because of this, all of Mark's memories come flooding back into his mind. Is she back? Can he find her? Can he rekindle their love? Some love gets a second chance, some don't. But ALL love is worth a second try. DANCING ALONE is a movie that anyone who has loved and lost love can relate to. And with an ending that may leave you in tears, it is not one to be missed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?125615</url></doc>
